flowchart TD
    U[User Tenant A] --> API[Shared API]
    API --> AUTH[AuthZ Layer]
    AUTH --> DAL[Data Access Layer]
    DAL --> DB[(Shared DB)]
    API --> CACHE[(Shared Cache)]
    API --> Q[(Shared Queue)]
    Q --> W[Worker]
    W --> DB

    T1[Tenant Context from token claim]
    T2[Tenant scope must exist on all reads and writes]

    AUTH -. validates .- T1
    DAL -. enforces .- T2
